{"word":"Ἀττικός","slug":"Ἀττικός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>Ἀττικός</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ἀκτή</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>Attic, Athenian</i>, <b>Solon</b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>ἡ Ἀττική</el> (<a href='S:scilicet'>sc.</a> <el>γῆ</el>), <i>Attica</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <el>Ἀτθίς.</el><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:Adverb'>Adv.</a> <el>-κῶς</el> <i>in Attic style</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}